Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:11.57,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs34}The way,if it's all predetermined.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:11.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs40}這條道路  是我命中注定的坎坷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾經許下誓言  要永遠和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,許下誓言讓我無比幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:18.79,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs34}And the way I should go all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:18.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs40}這條道路  是我一生必經的征程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想  我是喜歡他的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:27.42,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs34}I swear to go whatever will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:27.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs40}向天起誓  我將踏上旅途遠走高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這個心意  讓我感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾經告訴我  他會帶給我幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:35.13,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs34}Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:35.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs40}我所有過的恩典  將永遠留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他的這句話  令我感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:48.06,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs34}Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:48.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an9\fs40}我所有過的恩典  將永遠留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他把這麼多的幸福分給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,現在  無論別人怎麼說
